snippet: Gov. Nikki R. Haley tried to use a series of vetoes on state projects to move her conservative agenda, but legislators overrode many of them.
abstract: South Carolina Senate overrides a number of budget vetoes made by Gov Nikki R Haley, including arts funding and money for rape crisis centers; Haley has vetoed 81 items from the state budget in June, pleasing Tea Party residents but infuriating many others.
lead_paragraph: Gov. Nikki R. Haley tried to use a series of vetoes on state projects to move her conservative agenda, but legislators overrode many of them.

headline.seo: Gov. Nikki Haley’s Budget Ax Is Blunted by Legislators
headline.main: South Carolina Governor’s Budget Ax Is Blunted by Legislators
headline.print_headline: South Carolina Governor’s Budget Ax Is Blunted by Legislators
